snippet.title: Chronicles of 2 Heroes - Demo Gameplay
snippet.description: Short gameplay from the game Chronicles of 2 Heroes, a 16-bit Metroidvania set in feudal Japan. Developed by Infinity Experience and published by Catness Game Studios.
